== Faction ==
[[Mercenary Guild]]

== Location ==
The Orbie can be hired from the [[Outpost|Mercenary Guild Outpost]] in [[Vulcore]] for 12 mercreds.

== Combat Strategy ==
Having an Orbiter chassis allows the Controller to recover then repair any armor damage while patrolling. There are also several locations that have alternative potential outcomes when an Orbiter is present in the squad.

